          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p>Thinking like Keke:</p><p>117 out of 180 students said yes</p><p>↓÷1.8           ↓÷1.8</p><p>? out of 100 students said yes.</p><p><strong>65</strong></p>"
          ]
