      {
        "id": "GKsfrxw4nb-fOiI0",
        "title": "Text 3",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p><strong>Situation C. Winning a STEM Award</strong></p><p>A video of Mr. Satyam&#x27;s class won a STEM award for the students&#x27; work with the survey. Only 8% of the nominees won awards. There were 24 awards.</p><p>1. What is the total number of videos?</p>"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "3ESYsQvfHwpaSxo6",
        "title": "Text 14",
        "display": "teacher",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p>Students&#x27; strategies may vary. Using a 100 grid, students might shade 8 out of the 100 boxes to represent 8%. Then split the 24 awards among the 8 shaded boxes, so 3 in each box. Then, imagine that the box is full (100%) of the 3 videos per box. that would result in 300 total videos.</p>"
          ]
        }
      },
      [
        {
          "id": "v6nygoh35UushcmC",
          "title": "Text 15",
          "display": "teacher",
          "content": {
            "type": "Text",
            "format": "html",
            "text": [
              "<p>8 % represents 24 videos.</p><p>So every 1% represents 3 videos.</p><p>If the whole 100% was filled with 3 videos for each percent, it would be 300 videos.</p>"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "9SGTJX4u1Pm2tQXO",
          "title": "Movie grid",
          "display": "teacher",
          "content": {
            "type": "Image",
            "url": "cq/images/movie-grid.png",
            "filename": "cq/images/movie-grid.png"
          }
        }
      ],
      {
        "id": "6pITA5sjE3eY1XwE",
        "title": "Text 17",
        "display": "teacher",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p>The same reasoning could be represented using a scaling strategy as follows.</p><p>                         8% is 24 videos</p><p>                ÷1.8↓             ↓÷1.8</p><p>                            1% is 3 videos</p><p>                 ×100↓            ↓×100</p><p>                       100% is 300 videos</p>"
          ]
        }
      },
